  <title>xcb-util-wm-&xcb-util-wm-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      The xcb-util-wm package contains libraries which provide client and
      window-manager helpers for EWMH and ICCCM.
    </para>

